Experiment to keep workstation configuration under puppet control.

The goal is to have PGP-encrypted stuff even.  For now, I'm just
capturing the extra packages I've installed since setting up my
user.

	yum install -y rubygems
	gem install --no-ri --no-rdoc puppet
	useradd --system --user-group --no-create-home --uid 52 puppet
	puppet apply --modulepath modules --verbose manifests/axl.pp
